00:50:59,056 --> 00:51:00,475
Esther, chegamos.

476
00:51:03,478 --> 00:51:04,395
Esther?

477
00:51:51,067 --> 00:51:53,820
DET. DONNAN SE JUNTA À POLÍCIA
NA BUSCA POR ESTHER

478
00:51:53,903 --> 00:51:55,321
RUA OVERDALE, 371

