00:52:00,326 --> 00:52:01,828
Instituto Saarne?

480
00:52:13,631 --> 00:52:14,632
Esther?

481
00:53:11,355 --> 00:53:13,816
NÃO CORRESPONDE

482
00:53:57,568 --> 00:53:59,445
NÃO DESISTA DE MIM

